<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PersonNote/7> rdfs:label "Person Note: #7" ;
	a dprr:PersonNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cos. 49. If, as Sumner suggests, he was a younger brother of Lentulus Spinther (238). Cos. 57, his filiation should be P. f. L. n. (Orators 140-144); cf. T. P. Wiseman, JRS 65, 1975, 168. See below, on Lentulus Spinther." .
